The People of the State of Illinois, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Wesley Washington, Defendant-Appellant.(No. 59434;First District (5th Division)March 22, 1974.

BARRETT, J., took no part.

James J. Doherty, Public Defender, of Chicago (Richard Kharas, Assistant Public Defender, of counsel), for appellant.Bernard Carey, State’s Attorney, of Chicago (Kenneth L. Gillis and Mary Ellen Dienes, Assistant State’s Attorneys, of counsel), for the People. PER CURIAM.
